Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.79,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}果てしない空を往く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:41.24,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.77,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥か彼方、僕らを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:50.16,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ見ぬ未来へと‥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.54,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Always　 醒めきってた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.71,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}速すぎる  Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.83,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明な闇に囲まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も似た網の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.53,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Found you  あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:15.77,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れ動いたPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.20,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my past
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:22.19,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てキミに会うためのProcessだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.14,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.76,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.64,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.57,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鼓動奮わせて居たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.42,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.92,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.26,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光の中  目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.98,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.23,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.40,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.35,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえいま誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.00,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だからキミと Burst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------OPCHNlrc----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.79,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去往不断延展的天边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:41.24,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明的翅膀将我引领
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.77,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它在远方静待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:50.16,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞往未曾预见的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.54,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理智清醒时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.71,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}时常感到日夜流逝过快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.83,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}四周被透明的黑暗包围
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.32,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们都活在寸步难移的网中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.53,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻觅你  每当风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:15.77,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情仿佛随风跃动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.20,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:22.19,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆为与你相会的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.14,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.76,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.64,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}远方传来的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.57,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让我不禁加快心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.42,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.92,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.26,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光辉洒下  我逐渐苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.98,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你我互信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.23,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.40,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.88,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色将焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.35,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昔日伤痕亦成今日荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.00,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因此与你一起超越重力的束缚
